Title: Refúgio das Poldras
Location: Mondim de Basto, Vila Real District, Portugal
Description: O Refúgio das Poldras está situado em vilar de viando, mesmo junto ás margens do rio cabril, um dos rios mais limpos da região. Excelente para tomar banho, nadar, ou simplesmente caminhar ao longo de mais de 2km de margens e açudres . Está localizada a cerca de 2km do centro da vila caso pretenda fazer o percurso a pé pelo caminho romano. o bungalow dispõe de uma cama casal com vista única para a açudre, uma kitchenet para refeições ligeiras, casa de banho com chuveiro, e um deck suspenso.

Title: Relax on west slope Penha hill
Description: Quinta Milhão is a family farm located in Guimarães, a historical portuguese city considered the cradle of the nation. Surrounded by forest, sculptural granite rocks and blueberry plantation it is the perfect getaway for relaxation. The space Casa Nova is a modern house with one bedroom, one bathroom and one living room with kitchen and open space for more two guests. It can accomodate 4 adults, although it is more indicated for a family with two children or a couple. Our farm has more guesthouses and a beautiful garden with swimming pool, shared by all the guests. Normally swimming pool is open from May to September. Other things to note During blueberry harvesting, Quinta Milhão wakes up with sunrise! Normally, towards end of May and during June occurs the blueberry harvest. Blueberries contain severel nutrients, within which large quantities of antioxidants. Harvesting begins with sunrise, so that the fruit is at its best. It’s an experience! Learning how blueberries grow and go to our table. And of course, you could participate in this, as well as try them. License number 53904/AL

Title: Unik øy - Solholmen i Alverstraumen
Description: Ærverdige Solholmen i Alverstraumen har en unik historie, og har de siste årene blitt pusset opp og modernisert. 45 minutter nord for Bergen kan du nå leie din egen hytte på en egen øy. I ett av nøstene er det innredet med bord og stoler samt egen, privat pub, og kan derfor benyttes som både kurslokale for bedriftssamlingen og til private selskaper. På sommerstid er det muligheter for å sette opp partytelt i hagen.

Title: Restored Old Barn in a beautiful Galician valley
Description: This recently restored Old Barn is located in a green valley in north western Spain, only 7miles to the seaside and 1h. drive to Santiago de Compostela. It’s a unique place to enjoy tranquility, nature and to discover the authentic Galicia; a lush region with a mild climate, offering spectacular sceneries, sandy beaches, good sailing and surf, great hiking, historic gardens, golf, and a famed gastronomy mainly based in seafood, meats and the best white wines of the country.

Title: Superbe grange prestige
Description: Superbe Grange au cœur du village de GRUST. 10 mn station de ski Entièrement refaite: tout confort Salon cuisine de 80m², 2 chambres avec grand lit, 1 chambre avec 2 lits simples. Spa, salon extérieur, lieux magique.

Title: Yacht AquaMarina La Rochelle
Description: Yacht à louer à quai en plein centre ville de La Rochelle. Ce logement insolite se compose d'un beau salon lumineux avec écran plat, un coin repas, une cuisine équipée, deux suites avec lits deux personnes, deux cabines avec deux lits simples. Chaque cabine dispose de sa salle de bain. Une grande terrasse au pont supérieur, et une terrasse extérieure à l'arrière. Pour des raisons de sécurité à bord, la capacité du yacht est de 8 personnes maximum. caution de 5000€ sera demandé à l'arrivée.

Title: Open sky Pyramid
Description: Come to live an incredible experience at Mas Cabanids. Here, you can sleep on a Open Sky Pyramid to see the stars by night. This location is close to Perpignan, Spain, and Argelès sur Mer. The beach is situated at 15 kms. A peaceful area, a romantic moment... The Pyramid is our most incredible location in the Mas Cabanids in Maureillas las Illas.

Title: Lovely Studio
Description: The apartment was designed with all the needs of our guests in mind.

Title: Abrigo do Moleiro
Description: Classificado como monumento nacional, este emblemático moinho de Peniche teve, desde 1895 e durante décadas, utilização agrícola e industrial. Actualmente, completamente renovado e sob o nome “Abrigo do Moleiro” pretende ser um espaço acolhedor para turistas de todo o mundo proporcionando recordações únicas a quem nele pernoita. Para completar a experiência, os hóspedes recebem, ainda, o pequeno-almoço, entregue à porta.

Title: Lux Mare I
Description: Set over two levels of palatial splendor, this villa offers a breathtaking view of the Algarve coast and the shining Atlantic beyond. A truly magnificent poolside terrace lets guests enjoy Algarve mornings with peace and serenity assured. With room after room of spacious, considered design, this villa provides smart outfitting and deep comfort, plus the charm of nearby Lagos and numerous hidden beaches.

Title: Big Yurt Mountain View
Description: Peaceful Armonia Alpujarra Rentals is a truly special place. The location is at the foothills of the beautiful Sierra Nevada Mountains, in Andalucia, Spain, surrounded by olive and almond groves, with spectacular views.

Title: Tiny House Luna
Description: Das Da Silva Surfcamp ist ein typisch portugiesisches Landhaus in ruhiger Lage mit herrlichem Blick über die Landschaft bis zum Meer. Hier kommt zweimal täglich ein Hirte mit seiner Schafherde vorbei, morgens wird man vom Krähen eines Hahns geweckt und sonst hört man nur die Vögel zwitschern. Zum Strand läuft man zu Fuss in 20 Minuten, mit dem Beachcruiser, den man bei uns kostenlos ausleihen kann, dauert es nur 10 Minuten.

Title: Unique eco-friendly cabin surrounded
Description: With our cozy wooden cabin, you will feel like in a tree house.Shaded by cork oaks, you can enjoy the serene atmosphere from the deck or in our outdoor lounge where we will serve you a delicious breakfast (local, high quality/organic products). You can also swim in our lake.

Title: Olival e Sobreiro
Description: Perfect for couples or families with up to two children, our comfortable and modern 34 m2 modular wooden houses with an 8 m2 front deck. Our Eco-Suites are set on stakes, with a breath-taking view of the nearby valley and sea horizon.

Title: Chalé de madeira próximo ao Alqueva
Description: Bangalôs de madeira, com clima aconchegante e familiar, na parte exterior temos um parque infantil.

Title: TAMANCO TUBISMO
Description: Sleep in the round, wake up with songbirds and sunshine in our Tubismo Tube. We transformed eight reclaimed, concrete tubes into cosy rooms with a view. Plunge into our saltwater pool, escape to our garden-like campground and embrace the fresh air and a great night’s sleep under a starry night sky. Wether you are seeking refuge, looking to meet other travelers or hang out with friends: we have the right vibe for you!

Title: Monte da Casa do João
Description: Located in the beautiful hills of Santa Margarida da Serra, in Grândola, the Monte da Casa do João offers all the comfort of a luxury villa in the heart of the Alentejo countryside, surrounded by beautiful gardens, passion fruit orchards and the no less iconic Chaparros (cork oak trees)

Title: Amazing house with pool access
Description: This house, located in Águeda, is ideal for 7 vacationers. It offers 2 bedrooms, a pool access and WiFi.

Title: Vila Praia
Description: Construction Note: Please note that there is construction near to this villa. Please inquire with one of our Villa Specialists for further details.Traditional architecture, chic interiors and breathtaking ocean views are the picture-perfect backdrop to a holiday at Villa Praia. Part of the gorgeous Vila Vita Parc resort—known not just for its charming style but its fine dining and incredible spa—this contemporary vacation rental is close to great beaches, golf courses and more. Invite up to eight friends and family on a warm-weather getaway, or use this luxury residence for a honeymoon-style escape.

Title: Villa Breeze
Description: Follow a wide, cobbled drive to reach the crawling vine-covered façade of this elevated Costa del Sol escape. An intricately carved front door stands tall under the portico. Fragrant fruit and olive trees, sprinkled around the property, lend their unique scents to the fresh breeze. There are 2 world-class golf courses on the resort as well as tennis courts and a peaceful horseback riding centre.

Title: I TRULLI DI CAROLE
Description: Complex of authentic trulli entirely renovated preserving all the characteristics. Trulli Carole are located halfway between Ostuni and Martina Franca, surrounded by centuries-old olive and fruit trees. On the front of the house a stone paved area welcomes the swimming pool (mt 5x8) equipped with sun beds and special straw umbrellas; the outdoor kitchen with hob, barbecue and large table for outdoor dining.

Title: CASA CANALS - Villa para 10 personas en Mancor De La Vall.
Description: Lovely mansion in Mancor de la Vall, in the Tramuntana mountain range, with private pool and plenty of space for 10 people.

Title: PRINCESS V53
Description: Perfecta para disfrutar de las turquesas aguas de Ibiza y Formentera The space Dispone de Zodiac Williams, esquís, Wakeboard, equipo de Snorkeling
